title: Roller Coasters, USA, 2007
name: Roller Coasters, USA, 2007
description: To create this dataset, I took the physical addresses from all amusement parks with roller coasters listed on Roller Coaster Yellowpages, and found the latitude and longitude of each park.       To show the density of actual coasters, I entered the total number of roller coaster at each park in the Coasters" attribute.
